How It Works Add `showCommand: true` to
any action block: (wrap the above in a `
```action ` fence) The preview renders as
a `<pre>` element right below the button —
no interaction needed, always visible.
Pairs naturally with `{{VAR}}`
interpolation so the audience sees
resolved values, not raw variable names.

